<section class="section"><div class="shell"><p class="eyebrow">Process</p><h2>A focused path from operational noise to launchable system.</h2><ol class="workflow"><li>Audit the workflow, data owners, exceptions, and decision points.</li><li>Design the command grid with service rails, permissions, alerts, and reporting views.</li><li>Build the internal tool, integrations, dashboards, and AI assist layer.</li><li>Launch with documentation, training, QA checks, and support cadence.</li></ol></div></section>